    public static interface DataPropertyExpression.Super<D extends DataPropertyExpression>
extends DataProperty.Super<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty,D>, DataPropertyExpression
    The DataProperty.Super expression for a Descriptor whose ground is OWLDataProperty.

    It specifies how to querySuperDataProperties() and writeExpressionAxioms() for the DataProperties super over by the ground DataProperty (i.e.: OWLDataProperty).

      • writeExpressionAxioms

        default java.util.List<Axiom.MappingIntent> writeExpressionAxioms()
        Description copied from interface: Axiom.Descriptor
        This method is used to update the ontology with a specific Axiom.EntitySet (or Axiom.ExpressionEntitySet) by synchronizing the OWL representation with the internal state of the descriptor, such that they are equal. It is based on EntitySet#synchroniseTo(EntitySet).
        Specified by:
        writeExpressionAxioms in interface Axiom.Descriptor<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>
        Returns:
        the changes made in the OWL ontology during the writing. Note that the elements of the returned list, may have the Axiom.MappingIntent.getOntologyChanges() field initialised (i.e.: OWLOntologyChange).
